text: Alexandrovsky () is a rural locality (a khutor) in Krivle-Ilyushkinsky Selsoviet, Kuyurgazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 3 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 33 km from Yermolayevo, 10 km from Krivle-Ilyushkino. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kuyurgazinsky District
title: Alexandrovsky, Republic of Bashkortostan
